## 🎯 What to Do Next

### 1. Test Everything
- Create an account
- Try buying a bundle
- Check if payment modal appears

### 2. Customize Your Site
- Change colors in the CSS
- Add your own logo
- Update bundle prices
- Add more bundle options

### 3. Set Up Real Bundle Delivery
- Contact MTN or use a provider like:
  - Clubkonnect (https://www.clubkonnect.com/)
  - VTpass (https://vtpass.com/)
  - BuyPower (https://buypower.ng/)
- Get their API credentials
- Update the `deliverBundle` function in server.js

### 4. Deploy Your Website
See the main README.md for deployment instructions.

